HEADWORD: Rootstock
<hw>Root"stock`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A perennial underground stem, producing leafly stems or flower
stems from year to year; a rhizome.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

